        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "At last he reached a place where he could peep out and see that big, mossy, hollow log.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "When peter first saw him he was crouched on one end of the log, a fluffy ball of reddish brown, black and gray feathers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000004_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000004_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "He was resting.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000004_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000004_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "The outer edge was gray, then came a broad band of black, followed by bands of gray, brown and black. Around his neck was a wonderful ruff of black.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000004_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000004_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "His reddish brown wings were dropped until the tips nearly touched the log.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000004_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000004_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "He was of about the size of the little Bantam hens peter had seen in Farmer Brown's henyard.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000005_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000005_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "It was those fast moving wings that made the thunder.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000005_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000005_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "It was so loud that peter almost wanted to stop his ears.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000005_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000005_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "When it ended Strutter settled down to rest and once more appeared like a ball of fluffy feathers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000005_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000005_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "His ruff was laid flat.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "peter watched him thunder several times and then ventured to show himself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "Strutter threw out his chest proudly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"That is just what mrs Grouse says,\" he replied.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000007_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000007_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"I don't know of any better thunderer if I do say it myself.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"Speaking of mrs Grouse, where is she?\" asked peter eagerly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"Attending to her household affairs, as a good housewife should,\" retorted Strutter promptly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"Do you mean she has a nest and eggs?\" asked peter.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "Strutter nodded.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"She has twelve eggs,\" he added proudly.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"I suppose,\" said peter artfully, \"her nest is somewhere near here on the ground.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"It's on the ground, peter, but as to where it is I am not saying a word.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "It may or it may not be near here.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "Do you want to hear me thunder again?\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "Of course peter said he did, and that was sufficient excuse for Strutter to show off.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"I really would like to know where that nest is,\" said he to himself as he scampered along.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000016_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000016_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "Those eyes twinkled as they watched peter out of sight.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"That is what comes of having a cloak so like the color of these nice brown leaves.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000017_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000017_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "It is better than trying to hide a nest, and I certainly am thankful to Old Mother Nature for the cloak she gave me. I wonder if every one of these twelve eggs will hatch.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000017_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000017_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "If they do, I certainly will have a family to be proud of.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "Meanwhile peter hurried on in his usual happy go lucky fashion until he came to the edge of the Green Forest.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000018_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000018_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "It reminded him of Blacky the Crow, but he knew right away that it wasn't Blacky, because it was so much smaller, being not more than half as big.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"It's Creaker the Grackle.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000019_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000019_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "I believe Jenny Wren told me that he belongs to the Blackbird family.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000019_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000019_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "He looks so much like Blacky the Crow that I suppose this is why they call him Crow Blackbird.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"Why!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "Creaker the Grackle with the sun shining on him was truly beautiful.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000021_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000021_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "This changing of colors is called iridescence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000021_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000021_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "One other thing peter noticed and this was that Creaker's eyes were yellow.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"I'm glad you think so,\" replied Creaker.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000023_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000023_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"I'm not at all vain, but there are mighty few birds I would change coats with.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"Where is she now?\" asked peter.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000027_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000027_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"Over home,\" replied Creaker, pulling a white grub out of the roots of the grass.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000027_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000027_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "You know I am one of those who believe that every father should do his full share in taking care of his family.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"I'm glad to hear you say it,\" declared peter, nodding his head with approval quite as if he was himself the best of fathers, which he isn't at all.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"Ask as many questions as you like.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "I don't have to answer them unless I want to,\" retorted Creaker.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_142924_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/142924/133_142924_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"That is a very personal question,\" said he.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "CHAPTER EIGHT.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "HOW I RAN FROM THE WHITEBIRD CATCHERS.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "Yes, I may as well own to it: I was terribly frightened, but my first thoughts were as to what had become of my companions.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000004_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000004_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "Jack Penny and the doctor must have been seized at the same time as i Jimmy might have managed to escape.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "Perhaps his black skin would make him be looked upon as a friend.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "But the old captain, what about him?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000004_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000004_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "He would return to the schooner with his men and be seized, and knocked on the head for certain.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000004_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000004_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "The fierce resistance he would make certainly would cause his death, and I shuddered at the thought.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "Then I began thinking of my own friends, and then, very selfishly no doubt, about myself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "\"Well,\" I thought to myself, \"it is enough to scare anybody; but I'll try and let them see that I belong to a superior race, and will not show what I feel.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "My eyes kept wandering about eagerly, first to look where my companions were placed, but as I saw no sign of them I began to hope that they might have escaped; secondly, to see which would be the best course to take if I ran for my life.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "But for some little time I saw not the slightest chance of escape. There were too many savages close about me, and they must have divined my ideas, for they kept a watchful eye upon every act.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "At first I had felt numbed and cold.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "At last, after a great deal of incomprehensible chatter, it seemed that a decision had been come to about me, and a tall black armed with a war club came dancing up to me, swinging his weapon about, chattering wildly, and after a few feints he made a blow at my head.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "If that blow had taken effect I should not have been able to tell this story.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "But I had been too much with my friend Jimmy not to be well upon the alert.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000015_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000015_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "Jimmy's lessons were not thrown away.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "I was panting heavily, and a choking sensation came upon me, but I raced on, since it was for life.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-133_143240_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/133/143240/133_143240_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-133",
        "content": "How long the pursuit lasted I cannot tell.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
